{"tid":1383634,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得好灰心 但係一定要堅持！","createTime":"2019-07-29T17:33:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T17:51:27.000Z","uid":179925,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8fd5e2e2338c106c6e34c88f820e69ecac7afec7","tid":1383634,"uid":179925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:33:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>兄弟爬山 各自努力<span style=\"color: red;\"></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n之前遊行都有去 但一直都無沖前線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />原諒我未敢沖出去前線<br />\n<br />\n今日同家中深藍傾計 希望可以令佢地明白我地點解要咁做 我地唔係搞亂緊香港 傾個陣聽到句野令我真係覺得好氣餒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我：前線既人甚至係我地一直爭取緊既係香港人原本應該要享有既自由 大家一直為香港人爭取緊 佢地願意拎自己既前途出黎較飛.....<br />\n<br />\n深藍：拿 你聽清楚 我甚至我其他朋友都從無話要你地去爭取 我地無話要你地幫我地乜 我地無要求過<br />\n<br />\n我聽到之後真係唔知比咩反應 好心灰意冷 點解年輕人咁樣為大家付出 但仲有啲人可以毫無反應 甚至覺得係我地搞到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家我地可以心灰  但我地唔可以放棄 <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">加油各位付出緊既大家 我相信所有努力都會有成果<span style=\"color: maroon;\"></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"cd9f7f7b1ae0a5298d0ed6732491a652e13806f2","tid":1383634,"uid":179925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:36:06.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cad1535aa2cde7e9fed168eeb9233a92f67f9aa","tid":1383634,"uid":179925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:37:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0138e761348b3034ac3ba3cff8182abddff4d4f","tid":1383634,"uid":179925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:37:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d6df93630e6885fac032d2f321582bd4f9ca87f","tid":1383634,"uid":110851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:43:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n唔睇都埋嚟推下po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[集思廣益]香城online小地圖app<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1383244\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1383244</a>"},{"pid":"2bf84c5f7f1d160b4034e7bed3cd9acea48d3d09","tid":1383634,"uid":168596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:51:02.000Z","msg":"記得你出嚟係為咗自己認為啱嘅事發聲就可以了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6accf9fda02fd4b6ba6b15223ff1a4becf345c5d","tid":1383634,"uid":281418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:51:27.000Z","msg":"push"}]}